Date: Tue, 19 Apr 2016 10:38:49 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 17/85] MLK-12678 ARM: dts: imx6ull-ddr3-arm2: solve pin
 conflict for pwm3 and otg1

The pwm3 and otg1 share the same pin 'GPIO1_IO04'. And default,
the pin is used for otg1. So create a new dts file to solve
this conflict.

Signed-off-by: Fancy Fang <chen.fang@nxp.com>
[zou:Original patch taken from
git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-imx.git imx_4.1.15_2.0.0_ga]
Signed-off-by: zou cao <cao.zou@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/Makefile                    |    3 +-
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6ull-ddr3-arm2-lcdif.dts |   65 +++++++++++++++++++++++++
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6ull-ddr3-arm2.dts       |   46 -----------------
 3 files changed, 67 insertions(+), 47 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6ull-ddr3-arm2-lcdif.dts

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/Makefile b/arch/arm/boot/dts/Makefile
index 88aef02..d1adbe0 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/Makefile
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/Makefile
@@ -375,7 +375,8 @@ dtb-$(CONFIG_SOC_IMX6UL) += \
 	imx6ul-9x9-evk-csi.dtb \
 	imx6ul-9x9-evk-ldo.dtb
 dtb-$(CONFIG_SOC_IMX6ULL) += \
-	imx6ull-ddr3-arm2.dtb
+	imx6ull-ddr3-arm2.dtb \
+	imx6ull-ddr3-arm2-lcdif.dtb
 dtb-$(CONFIG_SOC_IMX7D) += \
 	imx7d-12x12-lpddr3-arm2.dtb \
 	imx7d-12x12-lpddr3-arm2-m4.dtb \
diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6ull-ddr3-arm2-lcdif.dts b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6ull-ddr3-arm2-lcdif.dts
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..8c30bb3
--- /dev/null
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6ull-ddr3-arm2-lcdif.dts
@@ -0,0 +1,65 @@
+/*
